The project is a word processor inspired by Microsoft WORD, pages and google doc.
Basic functions includes: Type and write.
                          Color selection, size selection, font selection.
                          Formation.
                          Italicize, underline, bold.
                          Word counter.
Click on each button when you want to implement the function, the word count counts it self.

